'''Jakub Tymiński 'Ominous'''' is the editor of The Polish Tolkienists Almanac ''[[Aiglos (journal)|Aiglos]]''. He was an associate from [[2013]] and has been the editorial secretary since [[September]] [[2014]].<ref>The editors of ''Aiglos'' http://aiglos.tolkien.com.pl/english/issues.php (accessed 3 September 2016)</ref> He has also contributed articles and artworks to the journal.
